text: Deepika Kumari is an Indian archer. She was born on 13 June 1994. Kumari competed at the 2012 Summer Olympics, 2016 Summer Olympics, and the 2020 Summer Olympics.Deepika KumariDeepika KUMARI == References == Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Indian archers Category:Olympians for India
